text: Point Reyes Station (formerly, Marin and Olema Station) is a small unincorporated town located in western Marin County, California. It is also the name of a census-designated place (CDP) in northern California covering the unincorporated town and surrounding countryside, with a total CDP population of 895. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in California Category:Census-designated places in California Category:Settlements in Marin County, California
title: Point Reyes Station, California
